data.body: This Inside the Wardrobe “Fashion Week Special”, finds blogger Susie Bubble at home as she prepares for Fashion Week. We get the inside scoop on what she’s planning to wear, what she’s packing and which shows she’ll be attending. Join us as we talk about Fashion Week essentials, discover how the perfect pair of glasses can shape an outfit, and find out what’s in her Fashion Week bag.

data.teaser: In this episode of Inside the Wardrobe, Style.com Fashion Director Yasmin Sewell shows us which Gucci jacket her five-year-old son keeps stealing from her, and tells us why everybody should have a sailor dress in their wardrobe.
